{"DamageImmunities":[],"ConditionImmunities":["Blinded","Deafened","Frightened","Poisoned"],"DamageResistances":[],"DamageVulnerability":[],"SavingThrowBonuses":[],"SkillBonuses":[],"_Senses":["Blindsight 120 ft.","Truesight 120 ft.","Darkvision 60 ft."],"_Languages":["All"],"_Abilities":[{"Title":"The Staff of Stars","Description":"The godking wields this Magic Quarterstaff that allows him to cast Heat Metal, Scorching ray, Fireball, Sickening Radiance, and wall of fire at will as though cast with a 4th level spell slot. The Staff also has 6 charges which recharge daily at midnight. The godking can use  one charge to cast Dawn, wall of light at their lowest level, Two charges to cast Sunbeam, Three charges to cast Crown of stars, Fire Storm, Prismatic spray, Five charges to cast Sunburst, or six charges to cast Meteor Swarm. If all six charges are used, The staff  becomes too hot to hold  or be near for 1d10 days, igniting flammable material it comes into contact with, flash-boiling water it makes contact with, causing all compasses within 40 miles to point toward it and all others within 100 miles to drift slightly toward it. Any creature that tries to hold onto the staff during this time takes 5d10 fire damage a round.  A creature that starts its turn within 5 feet of the staff takes 1d10 fire damage. The staff is thankfully indestructible.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Fey Ancestry","Description":"The Godking has advantage on saving throws against being charmed and Is immune to magical sleep","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Presence of Roots","Description":"Using his reaction on his turn, the Godking can extend the Tips of his subdermal roots to a creature he can see within 10 feet of him and deal 20 psychic damage","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Spreading Roots","Description":"As a Bonus action the Godking extends the roots under his skin out from his body where they drink from those around. Any creature that starts its turn within 10 feet of the Godking takes his Presence of roots damage. This lasts for one minute or until the Godking ends it willingly.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Symbiotic Entity & Wild Shape","Description":"The Kholirahi Godking can use this feature Twice between rests. The Godking Can Transform into a beast of CR 1 or less for 7 hours, They revert if they fall unconcious or reach 0 hp. The Godking retains his intelligence, Charisma, and wisdom and other abilities but loses the ability to cast spells, though he may continue to Concentrate on a spell he has already cast. The Godking may only speak or use his hands if his beast form allows him to do so. The rest of his stats and abilities are replaced with the beast's. His equipment merges with his new form\n\nAlternately the Godking can use this feature to gain 45 temporary hit points, doubles the damage of his Memory of roots feature, his melee attacks deal 1d6 poison damage to any target they hit. These benefits last or ten minutes","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"The Godking's Whim","Description":"Any humanoid slain by the Godking's Memory of Roots feature rises as a zombie with 18 hit points at the end of his turn and takes his turn immediately after the Godking. The godking takes no action to command it as it becomes an extension of his will","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"The Godking's Divinity","Description":"Critical hits don't do extra damage against the Godking","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0}],"_Actions":[{"Title":"Multiattack","Description":"The Godking Moseie makes 3 root  attacks.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Root attack","Description":": +18 to hit, reach 40 ft., Hit:  2d12+10 damage and the Target makes a DC 26 Wisdom Saving Throw or be Charmed by the Godking until the start of its next turn. Creatures who have been charmed this way are aware that magic was used to manipulate them.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0}],"_Reactions":[],"_Legendaries":[{"Traits":[{"Title":"Galaxy Chorus","Ability":"One Creature who can hear the god-king makes a DC 18 Charisma Saving Throw. On a failed save the creature is Incapacitated, blinded, deafened and is shown visions of a different universe. At the end of each of its turns, it may attempt to make the saving throw again, ending the effect on a success."},{"Title":"Staff of Stars","Ability":"The Godking casts Wall of Fire at 4th level"},{"Title":"Root Attack","Ability":"The Godking makes one Root Attack."}],"Title":"Legendary Actions"}],"_advancedSpells":[],"_advancedSpellData":[],"Title":"","STR":16,"DEX":16,"CON":20,"INT":24,"WIS":30,"CHA":20,"proficency":8,"Speed":"40 ft., burrow: 40 ft., climb: 40 ft., fly: 40 ft. (hover), swim: 40 ft.","AC":"16","HP":"170 (20d6 + 100)","CR":{"Index":28,"CR":"25","profBonus":8,"ArmorClass":19,"AttackBonus":12,"SaveDC":21,"LowHP":581,"HighHP":625,"XP":75000},"CreatureName":"Godking Moseie","CreatureSize":"Medium","CreatureType":"Humanoid (God-King)","CreatureAlign":"Neutral Evil","unique":true,"CreatureGender":"Male","LegendaryActions":"3"}